room_title: Escape room "Sabotage - at home" by EscapeSF in San Francisco
room_description: High tech escape-game-in-a-box within San Francisco Bay Area. Previously only available to large groups, the Sabotage spy case game has been modified to be enjoyed by teams of 2-5 from the safety of your home. Optionally multiple game cases can be delivered for larger groups. Contact us for games over multiple households.
